Class Device

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.Resource
      • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.FinalizedResource

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Hvac, LightSource, LoudSpeaker, MDS, Microphone, Sensor, Stereoset, Strap, TV, ValueDevice, VideoCamera

    public class Device
extends PhysicalThing
    Represents the class of physical manufactured things that have some capability. It adds no new property to physical things but just provides means for explicit distinction of certain physical things as devices.
    Author:
    mtazari
